
slash:  blocked by parry, allows damage through tackle/evade, deals 1 damage
evade:  effective against tackle
tackle: blocked by evade, allows damage through slash/parry, deals 1 damage
parry:  effective against slash

slash -> block
  +        |
  |        +
evade <- tackle

enemy1: [slash,  parry, tackle, parry]
enemy2: [block,  evade, parry,  parry]
enemy3: [tackle, slash, evade,  evade]

create minimal action ring buffer possible by choosing 4 action.
